<note id="fs-idm389462448" class="os-teacher">
<title>Suggested Sequencing</title>
<para id="fs-idm387779072">Use this Narrative with the <link document="m76411">Constitutional Convention</link> Lesson and after students have done <link document="m76420">The Articles of Confederation, 1781</link> Primary Source activity.</para>
